      "text": "There is being forwarded for the Bureau's information a copy of a letter from [REDACTED] USAF, AMC [REDACTED] Oak Ridge, Tennessee, to Mr. [REDACTED] U. S. Atomic Energy Commission, Oak Ridge. This letter is self explanatory and reveals that the photographs forwarded with referenced letter are the result of accident or purposeful hoax and are not actually photographs of a \"flying saucer\".",
